{
  "title": "Garlicky Creamy Thai Split Peas Curry",
  "description": "A creamy, garlicky and adventurous Thai dish featuring yellow split peas. Dairy-free-friendly and perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Thai",
  "diet": [
